description:
The revelations in the Electoral Bonds Scam are just starting - already there are questions regarding the veracity of the data supplied by the SBI & now they may be forced to submit the Bond Numbers. Prashant Bhushan in an extended conversation with The Deshbhakt talks about the next steps - including a Supreme Court mandated SIT into the scam and also why we need to take a hard look into the Election Commission works and why EVMs continue to be a source of concern.

